<h3><a href="http://www.stmgrts.org.uk/archives/2015/12/local_charity_appeals_for_the_sweetest_gift.html">Local charity appeals for the 'Sweetest Gift'</a></h3>

<img src="http://www.stmgrts.org.uk/images//Jeevika__bees_thumb.jpg" width="150" height="100" alt="Jeevika  bees" align="right" style="border: 1px solid #ccc; padding: 1px;" />

<p>Jeevika Trust, a small, Hampton Wick-based International Development charity, is appealing to the local community for help with an innovative project this Christmas. The organisation, in partnership with five carefully-selected Indian NGO partners, works to improve rural livelihoods in some of the most deprived regions of rural India through creating income generation opportunities for women and through improving access to clean water, better sanitation, better nutrition and improved healthcare for villagers.</p>

